HelloWorld
==========

Syntax highlighting

Java
```Java
Foo aiueo = new Foo(1234);
if (aiueo.getValue() == 1234) {
    System.out.println(aiueo);
}
```

C
```C
int aiueo = 1234;
if (aiueo == 1234) {
    printf("%d\n", aiueo);
}
```

PHP
```PHP
$aiueo = 1234;
if ($aiueo == 1234) {
    echo $aiueo, "\n";
}
```
